text: Sjan van Dijk (born 4 February 1964) is a Dutch archer. Van Dijk competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics.Sjan van DijkSjan VAN DIJCK == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
